 entered the evening and so has the dominion of Allah. All praise is due to Allah, there is no God but Allah alone without any partners.\u201d I think the Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11760,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/24\/dua-teach-me-beneficial-knowledge\/","url_meta":{"origin":11766,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: O Allah, teach me what will benefit me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, benefit me with what you have taught me, teach me what will benefit me, and increase my knowledge. All praise is due to Allah in every circumstance, and I seek refuge in Allah from\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33546,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/18\/shukr-praise-allah-fed-us\/","url_meta":{"origin":11766,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Praise be to Allah who fed us, sheltered us","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would say when he retired to his bed, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah who has fed us, given us drink, sufficed us, and sheltered us. How many are those who do not have enough and have no\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24171,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/14\/hamdulillah-food-drink-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":11766,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Eating: All praise to Allah who provided for us","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, ate or drank, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah who has fed us, given us drink, and has made us Muslims.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3457 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32848,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/21\/praise-allah-who-fed-me\/","url_meta":{"origin":11766,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eating: Praise be to Allah who fed me","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever eats a meal and says, \u2018All praise is due to Allah, who fed me this from his provision without any capability or strength on my part,\u2019 his previous minor sins will be forgiven.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25144,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/09\/dua-nawm-waking-up\/","url_meta":{"origin":11766,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for sleep, waking up","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, laid down at night, he would place his hand under his cheek and then say, \u201cO Allah, in Your name I die and I live.\u201d When the Prophet would awaken, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11766","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11766"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11766\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11766"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/